Change Log:
====================================================

version 6.1.0 
2017.06.15 -- Add query cache (result cache) 
2017.06.14 -- Add proxy_uuid column to meta tables
           -- Add meta tables for sharding templates & tables
2017.06.10 -- Add basic html auth for web interface
2017.06.09 -- Add "load config" command in admin interface
           -- Add "save config" command in admin interface (for sqltext & client ips)
2017.06.08 -- Add "proxy-user-local" for non global database users
           -- Add dedicate error log writer thread
           -- Add load config (backens, instances, groups) from mysql database

version 6.0.2
2017.06.06 -- Add sqlstats for each backend
2017.06.03 -- Add "min_idle_conn" option for minimum connection pool size
           -- Add "max_idle_conn" opiton for maximum connection pool size
2017.06.02 -- Change ping sql from "select" to "show variables" to avoid TCC control
           -- Add "high_session" option for slave high load protection
           -- Add "network_timeout" option for backend ping timeout
2017.06.01 -- Fix crash bug for monitor page (iptransdebug)
2017.05.25 -- Add long transaction audit feature
           -- Log the transaction for abnormal connection lost
2017.05.22 -- Auto choose the master when auto_readonly is on
2017.05.16 -- Fix crash issue when execute empty queries
2017.05.06 -- Set socket_file to "/tmp/oneproxy.sock" by default.
2017.05.05 -- Reserver the quote char ('"`) when rewriting queries.

version 6.0.1
2017.05.05 -- Write the process stack trace to log file when ternimate abnormally.
           -- Replace pipe with EV_TIMEOUT for thread event loop
           -- Abort the program with exit(-3) when any work thread terminate.
2017.05.04 -- Improve the load balance policy of slave query requests, more evenly.
2017.05.03 -- Fix assert error in parallel read result (CON_STATE_PARALLEL_READ_RESULT)
           -- Force query with "/*slave*/" hint to read from non-master node always
           -- Add "proxy-force-rowlimit" option to deny queries without limit clause
           -- Add "proxy-skip-network" option to disable work port during startup
2017.04.25 -- Add "proxy-ignore-readonly" to ignore read only transaction of spring framework
           -- Add "suppend force & resume" command in admin interface to disalbe working port temporary
2017.04.14 -- Print the client address for abnormal connection close in debug log
2017.04.13 -- Fix bug of lose transaction check for non partitioned DML operations.
           -- Add "proxy-loose-transaction" to enable cross server group DML operations.
           -- Set default value of "proxy-log-sqlerror" to on by default.
2017.04.12 -- Skip the transaction flag for global table's DML operation.
           -- Select jemalloc 4.0.4 and gperftool 2.5.0 as the default memorry allocator.
2017.04.09 -- Add "lazy-master" option to force queries in lazy transaction to run on master node.
           -- Replace long double with decNumber for better data precision (fix for long double precision lost)
2017.04.08 -- Make lazy transaction mode valid for non-sharding queries.
           -- Add "suggest_master" option to support read slave for master only query.

version 6.0.0
2017.04.01 -- Initialized from oneproxy 6.0.0


